author: COMSOL
description: Centrifugal pumps are used in various applications and can be found in many industries. The size of the pump in this model is typical for automotive applications. This model shows how to set up rotating machinery simulations using the frozen rotor approximation for modeling centrifugal pumps. The model Includes the computation of a series of interesting parameters for pumps using component couplings and especially evaluates the pump curve. The geometry is built with COMSOLâ€™s geometry tools.
